---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'; import Breadcrumbs from '../components/Breadcrumbs.astro'; import RelatedLinks from '../components/RelatedLinks.astro';
const faq={'@context':'https://schema.org','@type':'FAQPage',mainEntity:[
 {'@type':'Question',name:'What is the Ace Combat 8 preorder bonus?',acceptedAnswer:{'@type':'Answer',text:'Eligible preorders receive the playable F-14A Tomcat and an Ace Combat Zero: The Belkan War port for the purchased platform.'}},
 {'@type':'Question',name:'Is early access a preorder bonus?',acceptedAnswer:{'@type':'Answer',text:'No. Three-day early access is included with the Deluxe Edition; it is not listed as a general preorder bonus.'}},
 {'@type':'Question',name:'Can I play the Ace Combat Zero bonus on another platform?',acceptedAnswer:{'@type':'Answer',text:'The official listings describe platform-specific versions, so do not assume cross-platform entitlement.'}}
]};
---
<BaseLayout title="Preorder Bonuses — F-14A & Ace Combat Zero" description="Ace Combat 8 preorder bonuses explained: playable F-14A Tomcat and a platform-specific Ace Combat Zero port, plus what is not included."><Breadcrumbs items={[{label:'Preorder Bonuses'}]} /><article class="container article"><span class="eyebrow">Official Bandai Namco offer</span><h1>Ace Combat 8 Preorder Bonuses</h1><p class="direct-answer" data-concrete-answer>Eligible Ace Combat 8 preorders include two bonuses: the F-14A Tomcat as a playable aircraft and a port of Ace Combat Zero: The Belkan War for the platform where you buy the game. Three-day early access belongs to the Deluxe Edition, not the general preorder offer.</p>
<h2>Included with eligible preorders</h2><div class="card-grid"><section class="card"><span class="badge badge--confirmed">Aircraft</span><h3>F-14A Tomcat</h3><p>A playable aircraft bonus. The official offer does not establish that it is the only route to every Tomcat variant.</p><a href="/aircraft/f-14a">Open F-14A profile →</a></section><section class="card"><span class="badge badge--confirmed">Bonus game</span><h3>Ace Combat Zero: The Belkan War</h3><p>A port of the 2006 campaign tied to the purchased platform, with a smaller language list on Steam.</p><a href="/ace-combat-zero-bonus">Read the bonus guide →</a></section></div>
<h2>Platform and timing caveats</h2><p>PlayStation describes a PS5-ported version and Steam identifies a Steam version. Xbox store availability and regional offer terms should be checked on the checkout page. The publisher’s official game page sets a preorder deadline of October 1, 2026 at 11:59 PM local time and notes that bonus availability may end without notice.</p>
<h2>Do not confuse preorder and Deluxe benefits</h2><p>The Deluxe Edition separately includes three-day early access, the Ace Pass and additional content. Buying Standard during an eligible preorder window can qualify for the preorder items; buying Deluxe is the route to the edition benefits. Compare the current storefront terms before payment.</p>
<h2>Preorder FAQ</h2><div class="faq">{faq.mainEntity.map((x:any)=><section class="card"><h3>{x.name}</h3><p>{x.acceptedAnswer.text}</p></section>)}</div><aside class="source"><p class="mono">Evidence reviewed: July 18, 2026</p><ul><li><a href="https://www.bandainamcoent.com/games/ace-combat-8" rel="nofollow">Official Bandai Namco game page</a></li><li><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2288340/ACE_COMBAT_8_WINGS_OF_THEVE/" rel="nofollow">Official Steam listing</a></li></ul></aside></article><script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(faq)} /><RelatedLinks items={[{href:'/editions',label:'Compare Editions',desc:'Separate Standard, Deluxe and add-on content.'},{href:'/languages/ace-combat-zero',label:'Ace Combat Zero Languages',desc:'Check the six languages listed for the Steam port.'},{href:'/release-date',label:'Release & Early Access',desc:'See worldwide launch and Deluxe access timing.'}]} /></BaseLayout>
